Start-Up Process
Prerequisites:
- Visual Studio 2022
- .NET 8 SDK
- SQL Server Management Studio (SSMS)
Installation:
- Clone or download the repository.
- Open the solution (IoTAssetManagement2.sln) in Visual Studio.
- Execute the SQL scripts found in the DatabaseScripts folder to create and populate the database.
- Update the SQL Server connection string in appsettings.json to match your local SQL Server instance.
- Build and run the application.

